summary: This is my character in Skyrim Face Preset
descriptionHtml:
Edit: Someone just pointed out there was no file. It now exists. This was my bad 


This is a face preset for CBBE or designed around it. I do not know if it will work for other body mods as I do not use them. 



The hair is from Apachii Hair styles and eyes are from lideyes.   These can of course be changed by you if you wish. 

This Face Preset is also designed around the Female Nord.



How to install the preset

Go to your SKSE Folder
Go to Plugins\CharGen\Presets 

Drag and Drop the two files.



How to use the preset

Go into the game

Create a new character or for existing use race menu

Go to Sculpt and click on Import. 

Then that will be it.
